# FILE: adminDashboard/systemConfig/globalLayoutSettings.desc
# ROLE: Platform Visual & Logic Engine (Master Switches)
# ROUTE: /admin/config
# ACCOUNT: Admin only
# THEME: Dark · command-center · design token controls

## 1. HERO TERMINAL CONFIG (Home Page Control)
- Main H1 TEXTAREA: edits the hero headline across the site
- SEARCH QUICK TAGS: dynamic list builder for trending tags under search bar
  - Fields: [Tag Label] + [Target URL or Category]
- MOTTO TOGGLE: ON/OFF for "Challenge Every Day." global display

## 2. FREE PROMOTION ENGINE (Subscription Logic)
- GLOBAL STATUS: [🟢 فترة مجانية نشطة] | [⚪ مدفوع عادي]
- COUNTDOWN TIMER: date/time picker for promo end
- GLOW EFFECT TOGGLE: enables animated "مجاني" badge on /freelance/onboarding
- PRICE OVERRIDE: set subscription cost to $0 for new sign-ups in X days

## 3. ALERT BAR & BROADCASTS
- GLOBAL ALERT BAR: thin sticky top bar for urgent announcements
  - TEXT FIELD + COLOR PICKER: rose (تنبيه) · indigo (معلومة) · emerald (إيجابي)
- EXAM SEASON TOGGLE:
  - isExamSeason: true → News badge in header turns rose + pulse animation + redirects to /exam-hub
  - isExamSeason: false → normal behavior

## 4. DESIGN TOKENS
- All theme tokens match the current Tailwind @theme in index.css:
  - BG: #070C18 · Surface: #0F1828 · Border: #1E2D45
  - Accent: #6366F1 · Accent2: #8B5CF6 · Teal: #14B8A6
- ADMIN CAN ADJUST: accent color (with live preview)
- Glassmorphism intensity slider (controls blur on certain UI elements)
- Changes apply globally via CSS variable override

## 5. CONTACT & EXTERNAL NODES
- Social links management: WhatsApp · Telegram · Facebook
- ShamCash QR Update: upload new QR image + update payment note template
- Google Maps embed URL for /contact page

## 6. MAINTENANCE MODE
- [🛠️ وضع الصيانة] toggle
- Custom maintenance message textarea

## 7. ACTIONS
- [👁️ معاينة التغييرات] — opens site in new tab
- [🚀 تطبيق التغييرات عالمياً]
